John Company engages very seriously with its theme.
It is meant as a frank portrait of an institution that
was as dysfunctional as it was inﬂuential. Accordingly,
the game wrestles with many of the key themes of
imperialism and globalization in the eighteenth and
nineteenth centuries and how those developments
were felt domestically. As such, this game might not be
